{"tid":1062521,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐冠盃淘汰賽首輪數據：美斯浪射最多 C.朗拿度最多次過人","createTime":"2019-03-15T06:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T16:46:45.000Z","uid":25345,"like":69,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"08d99fffc993eaba523fe85b95d450c291bc2f67","tid":1062521,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:57:57.000Z","msg":"直播吧3月15日訊 香港時間3月14日，歐冠盃16強的比賽全部結束，歐冠盃八強全部出爐：曼聯（英超）、曼城（英超）、熱刺（英超）、利物浦（英超）、波圖（葡超）、祖記（意甲）、阿積士（荷甲）、巴塞（西甲）。<br />\n<br />\n賽後，著名數據網站Whoscored也統計了歐冠盃淘汰賽首輪數據，美斯以16次射門數據位居第一，根度簡傳球213次所有球員最多，C.朗拿度則有高達13次的過人數據。<br />\n<br />\n對此，Whoscored官推感歎道：「歐冠盃淘汰賽首輪，美斯（16次射門）和C.朗拿度（13次過人）的角色逆轉了。」<br />\n<br />\n歐冠盃淘汰賽首輪數據<br />\n<br />\n最多射門：美斯（巴塞隆拿）16次<br />\n<br />\n最多傳球：根度簡（曼城）213次<br />\n<br />\n最多關鍵傳球：塔迪奇（阿積士）10次<br />\n<br />\n最多過人：C.朗拿度（祖雲達斯）13次<br />\n<br />\n最多攔截：奧塔維奧（波圖）11次<br />\n<br />\n最多斷球：馬茲拉維（阿積士）9次<br />\n<br />\n最多成功爭頂：迪施高（羅馬）16次<br />\n<br />\n最多解圍：吉文尼斯斯（馬德里體育會）17次<br />\n<br />\n最多撲救：奧納納（阿積士）13次"},{"pid":"ec0e6c64ba430a6ee7ea6a56c19aa47725b10898","tid":1062521,"uid":33660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca3ab9881e51beeda3510c3634c73542fd02d35","tid":1062521,"uid":4618,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T07:11:23.000Z","msg":"過唔到人唔計"},{"pid":"f23c428139894744284ec52892bf5ad47736b9c6","tid":1062521,"uid":43063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T07:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阿積士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14f6c4a8ee32a84d6546133d